<P>__{(shrugging)}
<D>__{they got it an a long playing record now music to string her along by. my wife doesn't understand me we haven't gotten along for years you're the best thing that ever happened to me }
<C>__{sheldrake}
<D>__{that's enough, fran.}
<C>__{fran}
